<br>
And a level 8 somethingorother lizard proceeds to beg from her.  First buffs, then stuff (she's naked dammit, check out the pink panties!), then just trailing along behind her KSing her.<br>
<br>
I tell her...<br>
<br>
'you can tell him to fuck off, you know'<br>
<br>
'I can???'<br>
<br>
'you can'<br>
<br>
You have gotten better at maniacal laughter (2)<br>
<br>
