<br>
Rummage in my packs (and those of all of my twinks).  Force a friend to log in and carry all this crap, and take myself and a low level paladin to Field of Bone to deliver the goods.  The leezard is just tickled to bits that we would come and see her.  There are all of 5 lizards in the zone.  After I remove invis, there are 4 lizards bouncing around us begging for buffs, and one going 'omfg go the hell away ALL of you!!' (screaming at the monitor is not effective, but I wasn't going to tell her that).<br>
<br>
Annoying_leezard_01:  Can I have some pp?<br>
<br>
Jaylana:  no<br>
<br>
(GF laughs from behind me on the couch)<br>
<br>
proceed to hand MY leezard more pp than she'll need for a while<br>
<br>
