<br>
proceed to hand MY leezard 2 bags of gear and help her get dressed<br>
<br>
Annoying_leezard_01:  Can I have some buffs?<br>
<br>
Jaylana:  no<br>
<br>
proceed to buff my GF to within an inch of her eyeballs.<br>
<br>
::cast improved superior camo::<br>
<br>
